jssimide is an opensource JiST/SWANS and ns2 based network simulator and IDE from making it easy to write new protocols at different layers of tcp/ip stack
and also experimet with protocol behaviuors and collect some usefull simulator statistics by constructing wired,wireless and combination of wired and wirelss
networks very easily.

It also has an jsanim which enables users to easily animate the senarios.  
